  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take part in the fight for humanity's freedom in AI Olympius!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the resistance and conquer the top of Olympus of the artificial intelligence that has equated itself to a god in a story-driven third-person shooter with RPG elements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478970/extras/cc8fb0c154862e3b3b52c7a7330c6420.avif?t=1769693199\" width=626 height=250 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Variability of the world</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game's missions occur in different parts of the planet, so each sector differs from the previous one.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478970/extras/4f53a0d1c1301f46f6f89267db43e91c.poster.avif?t=1769693199\" width=800 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478970/extras/4f53a0d1c1301f46f6f89267db43e91c.webm?t=1769693199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478970/extras/4f53a0d1c1301f46f6f89267db43e91c.mp4?t=1769693199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Early access</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game has 28 campaign missions available for about 30 hours of gameplay. Another part of the story is in development. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rebel technologies</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect resources, develop your character, improve your skills, and unlock new abilities to fight artificial intelligence.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game offers over 60 weapon and costume modifications</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478970/extras/6649155167ae95deaba82c126c834afe.avif?t=1769693199\" width=626 height=250 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play together</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game supports two-player co-op in split-screen mode on the same computer or simple network connection.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478970/extras/1789c0130f3a9b8635541cbb1b300331.poster.avif?t=1769693199\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478970/extras/1789c0130f3a9b8635541cbb1b300331.webm?t=1769693199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478970/extras/1789c0130f3a9b8635541cbb1b300331.mp4?t=1769693199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mind control</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Capture enemy robots, or make allied machines right on the battlefield.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478970/extras/1c4d0c84f7535efcb302a366c3eb685c.poster.avif?t=1769693199\" width=600 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478970/extras/1c4d0c84f7535efcb302a366c3eb685c.webm?t=1769693199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478970/extras/1c4d0c84f7535efcb302a366c3eb685c.mp4?t=1769693199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Base building</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create, defend, and improve your base to extract resources in the additional game mode intertwined with the main storyline.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take part in the fight for humanity's freedom in AI Olympius!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the resistance and conquer the top of Olympus of the artificial intelligence that has equated itself to a god in a story-driven third-person shooter with RPG elements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478970/extras/cc8fb0c154862e3b3b52c7a7330c6420.avif?t=1769693199\" width=626 height=250 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Variability of the world</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game's missions occur in different parts of the planet, so each sector differs from the previous one.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478970/extras/4f53a0d1c1301f46f6f89267db43e91c.poster.avif?t=1769693199\" width=800 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478970/extras/4f53a0d1c1301f46f6f89267db43e91c.webm?t=1769693199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478970/extras/4f53a0d1c1301f46f6f89267db43e91c.mp4?t=1769693199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Early access</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game has 28 campaign missions available for about 30 hours of gameplay. Another part of the story is in development. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rebel technologies</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect resources, develop your character, improve your skills, and unlock new abilities to fight artificial intelligence.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game offers over 60 weapon and costume modifications</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478970/extras/6649155167ae95deaba82c126c834afe.avif?t=1769693199\" width=626 height=250 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play together</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game supports two-player co-op in split-screen mode on the same computer or simple network connection.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478970/extras/1789c0130f3a9b8635541cbb1b300331.poster.avif?t=1769693199\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478970/extras/1789c0130f3a9b8635541cbb1b300331.webm?t=1769693199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478970/extras/1789c0130f3a9b8635541cbb1b300331.mp4?t=1769693199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mind control</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Capture enemy robots, or make allied machines right on the battlefield.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478970/extras/1c4d0c84f7535efcb302a366c3eb685c.poster.avif?t=1769693199\" width=600 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478970/extras/1c4d0c84f7535efcb302a366c3eb685c.webm?t=1769693199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1478970/extras/1c4d0c84f7535efcb302a366c3eb685c.mp4?t=1769693199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Base building</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create, defend, and improve your base to extract resources in the additional game mode intertwined with the main storyline.</p>",
